data.description: Can you find a better setting for entertainment? This amazing home has it all! The back yard is set up for full entertainment. Fenced backyard with additional privacy fencing, a covered patio, beautiful custom inground pool & spa, covered patio, & outdoor wood burning fireplace, newly installed gazebo and pet friendly turf for low maintenance yard work. The 2-level home is loaded, with high ceilings, large living room with gas fireplace, great views and access directly to the backyard. Large kitchen opens to breakfast nook, quartz counters, gas stove, stainless appliances, prep island, lots of cabinets, ample counter space and pantry. An additional office near entry and a formal dining space. Master suite on the 1st w/double sinks, tile shower, separate soaking tub & vanity w/private access to the pool/covered patio. 2nd Master, additional bedrooms on upper-level w/ open railing with a large landing to living room & large bonus room over the 2-car garage. Great home located
